                                <p class="help-block">这里是你帐号的昵称，建议用真实名字</p>
                            </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="birth">我们的合照头像：</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <p>
                                <img id="imgAvatar"  width="196" height="136" alt="" src="@avatarUrl" />
                                <input type="hidden" value="@lover.Avatar" name="avatar" id="avatar" />
                            </p>
                            <div id="divUploadAvatar"></div>
                            <span class="field-validation-error" data-valmsg-for="avatar" id="tips-avatar" data-valmsg-replace="true"></span>
                            <p class="help-block">请上传一张你们的合影照片，建议比例是196px×136px，大小不能超过1MB（不可更改）</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
